1
00:00:10,967 --> 00:00:12,700
<i>I'm not going
to confess anything!</i>

2
00:00:12,833 --> 00:00:14,433
<i> You, monster!</i>

3
00:00:14,567 --> 00:00:15,533
<i>- You really are Olive!
- Danilo!</i>

4
00:00:15,667 --> 00:00:17,300
<i> You took our daughter!</i>

5
00:00:18,533 --> 00:00:20,033
<i> Mookie!</i>

6
00:00:20,167 --> 00:00:20,700
<i> Zayn.</i>

7
00:00:20,833 --> 00:00:21,767
<i> What happened to Mookie?</i>

8
00:00:21,900 --> 00:00:23,433
<i>We need to bring her
to the hospital.</i>

9
00:00:23,567 --> 00:00:24,433
<i> The brake is not working.</i>

10
00:00:24,567 --> 00:00:25,767
<i> What?</i>

11
00:00:25,900 --> 00:00:27,667
<i>- Sir, what are you doing to me?
- Miss!</i>

12
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:31,067
<i>I need to kill whoever gets
in the way of my plans!</i>

13
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:32,200
<i> Logan. Mookie!</i>

14
00:00:32,333 --> 00:00:34,200
<i> No one loves me.</i>

15
00:00:34,367 --> 00:00:35,667
<i> Someone will love you.</i>

16
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:37,700
<i> But you're the one I love.</i>

17
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,667
Let me go!

18
00:01:21,033 --> 00:01:22,433
Hey!

19
00:01:22,567 --> 00:01:24,700
Caloy, can you quiet
that kid down?

20
00:01:24,833 --> 00:01:26,833
I can't think!

21
00:01:26,967 --> 00:01:29,933
Let me go!
I don't have a murderer mom!

22
00:01:30,067 --> 00:01:31,533
- Shut up!
- Let me go!

23
00:01:31,667 --> 00:01:32,700
You're so evil!

24
00:01:32,833 --> 00:01:34,633
You said you love me!

25
00:01:34,767 --> 00:01:37,033
And this is what you do to me?

26
00:01:37,167 --> 00:01:40,533
You can scream all you want,
no one will hear you!

27
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:43,033
So shut up before
I lose my patience!

28
00:01:43,167 --> 00:01:45,300
I won't shut up!

29
00:01:45,433 --> 00:01:47,500
- Oh, you won't shut up?
- I won't shut up!

30
00:01:47,633 --> 00:01:49,900
- You won't shut up?
- What are you going to do?

31
00:01:50,033 --> 00:01:51,667
You won't shut up?

32
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:56,300
You're so stubborn.

33
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,700
Come on, Caloy.

34
00:02:00,833 --> 00:02:02,667
We need to go. Hurry up!

35
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:05,100
So that Emma can't follow us.
Hurry!

36
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:08,433
Ma'am.

37
00:02:08,567 --> 00:02:10,433
What are you waiting for?

38
00:02:10,567 --> 00:02:14,333
Get in the car. We need to get
away before Emma catches us.

39
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:16,633
Ma'am, I'm sorry, but...

40
00:02:16,767 --> 00:02:18,000
I'm getting scared.

41
00:02:19,033 --> 00:02:20,767
What if her parents catch us?

42
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:22,967
That's why we need to go now!

43
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,900
We need to get
to a faraway place

44
00:02:25,033 --> 00:02:26,433
so we won't be followed.

45
00:02:26,567 --> 00:02:27,800
Hurry up!

46
00:02:28,333 --> 00:02:30,233
Ma'am, my conscience
can't take it anymore.

47
00:02:31,467 --> 00:02:32,600
Conscience?

48
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:34,033
Okay,

49
00:02:34,167 --> 00:02:37,033
I'll triple the payment so that
your conscience gets paid too.

50
00:02:37,167 --> 00:02:39,967
You don't want it? Fine.

51
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:42,833
I'll triple the payment,
or I'll bury you?

52
00:02:42,967 --> 00:02:44,833
Ma'am, please don't do that.

53
00:02:44,967 --> 00:02:47,767
I'll just return all the
money you gave me, Ma'am.

54
00:02:47,933 --> 00:02:50,333
My conscience can't take it
anymore. I can't do this.

55
00:02:51,333 --> 00:02:53,067
Ma'am, please don't do that.

56
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,067
Ma'am.

57
00:03:05,967 --> 00:03:08,067
Hello, Andong.
Come and pick me up.

58
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,233
I'll send you
the pinned location.

59
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,533
Okay. Okay, okay. Thank you.

60
00:03:17,667 --> 00:03:18,667
What did she say?

61
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,200
They had an accident on
their way to the hospital.

62
00:03:22,367 --> 00:03:24,100
- What?
- What?

63
00:03:24,233 --> 00:03:25,133
They had an accident?

64
00:03:25,267 --> 00:03:27,367
Yes, but they're okay.

65
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,433
But...

66
00:03:28,567 --> 00:03:30,100
it's Mookie...

67
00:03:30,233 --> 00:03:32,233
Olive kidnapped her again.

68
00:03:32,367 --> 00:03:34,633
Is this never-ending?

69
00:03:36,367 --> 00:03:38,900
That explains why I'm like
a worm swiggling around.

70
00:03:39,033 --> 00:03:40,000
I'm so restless.

71
00:03:40,133 --> 00:03:42,333
My child,
who is Satan's daughter,

72
00:03:42,467 --> 00:03:45,067
is doing something evil again.

73
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:55,633
Andong, hurry up. Go get Mookie.

74
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,667
Bring her to the car. Hurry!

75
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,567
Over here!

76
00:04:14,367 --> 00:04:15,433
Move faster!

77
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:44,267
Hi, baby girl.

78
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:48,100
You're here in my sanctuary.

79
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:53,533
In a peaceful and quiet place.

80
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:59,033
Mommy, I don't want it here.
Please.

81
00:04:59,167 --> 00:05:00,700
Mookie, don't worry.

82
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:04,567
You're safe with me.

83
00:05:04,700 --> 00:05:06,900
Because I'm your doctor.

84
00:05:07,033 --> 00:05:09,133
But you're not a real doctor.

85
00:05:09,267 --> 00:05:12,667
- And you're not my parent.
- I'll do everything

86
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,800
- for you, Mookie!
- Mommy, no! I don't want to!

87
00:05:14,933 --> 00:05:16,400
- Please, Mookie!
- I don't want to! Mommy, no!

88
00:05:16,533 --> 00:05:19,133
I don't want us to be separated
again. Mookie, please.

89
00:05:19,267 --> 00:05:24,133
- Please!
- I was never happy before.

90
00:05:24,267 --> 00:05:26,467
The truth is,

91
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:30,433
I've been doing that
to forget Mommy Emma.

92
00:05:30,567 --> 00:05:32,667
But I still want
our family to reunite.

93
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:35,800
Because I still want Mommy Emma,
not you!

94
00:05:35,967 --> 00:05:37,333
Enough!

95
00:05:37,467 --> 00:05:39,767
Enough, Mookie! Enough!

96
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:46,700
I'm doing everything I can,
right?

97
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:52,267
So you can love me!
But why can't you still do that?

98
00:05:57,267 --> 00:06:02,033
I'm doing everything
to love and care for you.

99
00:06:04,467 --> 00:06:06,533
Yes, I admit.

100
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:13,633
I was overprotective of you,
Mookie.

101
00:06:13,767 --> 00:06:18,267
And that's because nobody
protected me as a child.

102
00:06:27,467 --> 00:06:29,867
Someone took Jade and me in.

103
00:06:32,533 --> 00:06:34,933
They adopted us.

104
00:06:38,233 --> 00:06:42,100
But I still haven't experienced
the love and care

105
00:06:42,267 --> 00:06:44,067
I've always dreamed of.

106
00:06:46,167 --> 00:06:50,200
Maybe that's why
I don't know how to love you.

107
00:06:52,567 --> 00:06:54,000
But just like what I said...

108
00:06:56,133 --> 00:06:57,900
I'll make it up to you.

109
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,267
We'll be happy again...

110
00:07:04,033 --> 00:07:05,767
with your dad.

111
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:08,567
You know what...

112
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:14,200
if you can only accept
that you're sick

113
00:07:14,367 --> 00:07:19,500
and you need to get treated,
you'll get better soon, Mommy.

114
00:07:19,633 --> 00:07:20,500
No!

115
00:07:20,633 --> 00:07:22,367
We'll be happy.

116
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:25,267
-No!
-Everything will go well, Mommy.

117
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,600
- So, please.
- No.

118
00:07:27,733 --> 00:07:30,167
Promise, Mommy.

119
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:34,567
I won't let us
get separated again!

120
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:37,967
Never, Mookie. Never.

121
00:07:48,867 --> 00:07:51,767
I have a brilliant idea.

122
00:07:55,533 --> 00:07:58,500
I know what to do.

123
00:08:00,033 --> 00:08:03,600
So that you'll forget
your Mommy Emma.

124
00:08:03,733 --> 00:08:05,200
No...

125
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:08,900
- Mommy.
- Just a single shot.

126
00:08:09,033 --> 00:08:11,333
One single dose.

127
00:08:11,467 --> 00:08:13,533
You won't get hurt.

128
00:08:13,667 --> 00:08:15,167
No symptoms.

129
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:18,733
- No after effects.
- No, no. Please.

130
00:08:18,867 --> 00:08:21,733
- After that, Mookie...
- Mommy!

131
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:26,900
- we'll be close again.
- Please! Stop this!

132
00:08:27,033 --> 00:08:27,933
Mommy, I don't want this!

133
00:08:28,067 --> 00:08:31,200
It's just going to be
you and me forever!

134
00:08:31,333 --> 00:08:33,300
No!

135
00:08:33,433 --> 00:08:36,133
Yes! Yes, that's right!

136
00:08:36,267 --> 00:08:38,967
You're so smart, Olive!

137
00:08:39,100 --> 00:08:40,933
Please, help me!

138
00:08:41,067 --> 00:08:41,933
But...

139
00:08:42,067 --> 00:08:43,800
Help me.

140
00:08:43,933 --> 00:08:45,500
You're crazy.

141
00:08:45,633 --> 00:08:47,267
Something seems missing.

142
00:08:55,033 --> 00:08:58,833
No!

143
00:08:58,967 --> 00:09:01,900
I don't know if I'm still
doing the right thing.

144
00:09:03,033 --> 00:09:05,467
But...

145
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,867
I have no one else to rely on.

146
00:09:11,333 --> 00:09:12,633
A drug vial.

147
00:09:13,867 --> 00:09:15,867
I'll text you its name

148
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:19,400
and the address
where you'll send it.

149
00:09:19,533 --> 00:09:22,267
But the million dollar
question is...

150
00:09:24,533 --> 00:09:28,133
can I still trust you, Astrid?

151
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:32,967
Remember...

152
00:09:33,100 --> 00:09:34,300
no police.

153
00:09:34,433 --> 00:09:36,000
Mommy...

154
00:09:36,133 --> 00:09:39,467
If you don't want anything bad
to happen to Mookie.

155
00:09:42,333 --> 00:09:45,633
Help me!

156
00:09:45,767 --> 00:09:50,200
Help me, please!

157
00:10:10,267 --> 00:10:13,300
Ma'am, excuse me.
Is someone going with us?

158
00:10:13,433 --> 00:10:15,933
- We'll just follow you.
- Okay.

159
00:10:26,233 --> 00:10:28,500
Maybe no one really loved him.

160
00:10:30,067 --> 00:10:33,133
That's why, even though
he fooled and betrayed me,

161
00:10:33,267 --> 00:10:34,833
I can't get mad at him.

162
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:39,567
I'm indebted to Logan.

163
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:43,367
If it weren't for him,
I would've gone astray.

164
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:44,467
And now...

165
00:10:45,533 --> 00:10:48,467
he has died because of me.

166
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,633
Emma...

167
00:10:51,267 --> 00:10:53,033
don't blame yourself.

168
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:57,167
It's my fault, too.

169
00:10:57,300 --> 00:10:59,133
I let Jade persuade me.

170
00:10:59,267 --> 00:11:01,833
If I tried to understand you,

171
00:11:01,967 --> 00:11:04,100
cared for you,

172
00:11:04,233 --> 00:11:06,067
and stayed by your side...

173
00:11:08,133 --> 00:11:10,500
these things wouldn't happen.

174
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:13,467
Emma...

175
00:11:14,667 --> 00:11:16,133
I'm sorry.

176
00:11:17,933 --> 00:11:20,567
I'm sorry for getting mad at you

177
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:23,800
and for not believing you.

178
00:11:23,933 --> 00:11:25,800
Please forgive me.

179
00:11:27,133 --> 00:11:28,700
Dan...

180
00:11:28,833 --> 00:11:31,367
we all made a mistake here.

181
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:35,967
And Olive won't stop
until she ruins our family.

182
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:39,267
So promise me.

183
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:41,800
We won't fall victim
to her again.

184
00:11:41,967 --> 00:11:43,733
We won't argue again.

185
00:11:43,867 --> 00:11:45,567
We won't get separated again.

186
00:11:46,733 --> 00:11:49,600
Dan, let's work together

187
00:11:49,733 --> 00:11:51,267
for Mookie's sake.

188
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:17,033
Hello, Zayn?

189
00:12:17,167 --> 00:12:18,033
<i> Aunt Emma!</i>

190
00:12:18,167 --> 00:12:20,600
<i>Miss Astrid told us
where Mookie is!</i>

191
00:12:20,733 --> 00:12:22,967
<i>The police are going there
and I'm coming with them.</i>

192
00:12:24,300 --> 00:12:26,333
We'll follow you.

193
00:12:26,467 --> 00:12:28,233
Dan, it's about Mookie.

194
00:12:28,367 --> 00:12:29,367
Where is she?

195
00:12:29,667 --> 00:12:31,233
Please, Mommy.

196
00:12:32,033 --> 00:12:34,533
Aunt Astrid! Aunt Astrid!

197
00:12:34,667 --> 00:12:36,900
- Aunt Astrid, please!
- Oh, there you are,

198
00:12:37,033 --> 00:12:39,733
my trusted sidekick.

199
00:12:39,867 --> 00:12:42,200
Well, of course,
I'm going to be honest with you.

200
00:12:42,467 --> 00:12:45,300
My trust in you
has lessened a bit.

201
00:12:45,433 --> 00:12:47,800
That's why I had you monitored.

202
00:12:47,967 --> 00:12:50,900
But I heard that you came alone.

203
00:12:52,033 --> 00:12:54,367
So, let me ask you again,
Astrid.

204
00:12:55,967 --> 00:12:58,067
Can I trust you?

205
00:12:59,133 --> 00:13:00,833
Of course.

206
00:13:00,967 --> 00:13:04,000
I was happy when I learned that
you're not Jade.

207
00:13:04,133 --> 00:13:06,633
That my friend is still alive.

208
00:13:06,767 --> 00:13:08,067
That you're still alive.

209
00:13:11,067 --> 00:13:12,600
I'm so touched.

210
00:13:14,633 --> 00:13:16,533
You know what...

211
00:13:16,667 --> 00:13:21,500
I really want to believe
that I can trust you, Astrid.

212
00:13:21,667 --> 00:13:24,033
You know...

213
00:13:24,167 --> 00:13:26,367
you're my only friend.

214
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:29,633
Friend?

215
00:13:29,767 --> 00:13:31,667
You see me as a friend?

216
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:36,600
Well to be honest, Astrid,

217
00:13:36,733 --> 00:13:39,267
I treat you more than
as a friend.

218
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:43,267
Out of all people,
you're the only one who knows

219
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:46,600
that I don't have a family
that loves me. Right?

220
00:13:46,733 --> 00:13:50,000
That's why I treated you
more than a friend.

221
00:13:50,133 --> 00:13:52,600
You're like a family to me.

222
00:13:56,267 --> 00:13:58,433
Here's the memaristol (medicine
that can erase memories).

223
00:13:58,567 --> 00:14:02,033
It's a good thing we still
have stocks in Artemis.

224
00:14:02,167 --> 00:14:03,633
Perfect.

225
00:14:13,267 --> 00:14:15,500
But I did some research.

226
00:14:15,633 --> 00:14:18,900
I read that it erases memories.

227
00:14:19,033 --> 00:14:22,600
Olive, where will you use that?

228
00:14:22,733 --> 00:14:24,533
Don't tell me...

229
00:14:26,133 --> 00:14:27,467
Yup...

230
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,833
it's for Mookie.

231
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:33,867
Because I want to erase
all her memories...

232
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:37,700
No!

233
00:14:37,833 --> 00:14:39,367
No, please!

234
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:42,200
Mommy, no!

235
00:14:42,333 --> 00:14:46,667
I'd rather die
than forget Mommy Emma!

236
00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:49,933
No matter what happens,
I will never forget her!

237
00:14:50,067 --> 00:14:52,333
You're so evil!

238
00:14:52,467 --> 00:14:54,733
Please help me! Please!

239
00:14:54,867 --> 00:14:57,133
Please! I don't want this!

240
00:14:57,267 --> 00:14:59,400
Don't worry, Mookie.

241
00:14:59,533 --> 00:15:01,067
This will be quick.

242
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,333
Olive...

243
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:06,700
Mookie might get crazy
if you inject that into her.

244
00:15:06,833 --> 00:15:09,233
Of course not.

245
00:15:09,367 --> 00:15:10,833
You know what, Astrid?

246
00:15:10,967 --> 00:15:13,300
That's what I miss about you.

247
00:15:13,433 --> 00:15:16,067
You still feel guilty.

248
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:19,733
But I know that
even if you feel guilty,

249
00:15:19,867 --> 00:15:22,433
you will still do what I want.

250
00:15:22,567 --> 00:15:27,000
- Right?
- Help me, please!

251
00:15:29,233 --> 00:15:32,100
- Are you ready, my sweetheart?
- No!

252
00:15:32,233 --> 00:15:35,200
- Let's do this.
- No, no, no.

253
00:15:35,367 --> 00:15:36,433
Please.

254
00:15:36,567 --> 00:15:37,967
No!

255
00:15:38,100 --> 00:15:39,100
Mommy!

256
00:15:48,167 --> 00:15:50,367
It wasn't so bad, right?

257
00:16:02,933 --> 00:16:05,167
You're going to be fine, Mookie.

258
00:16:06,767 --> 00:16:08,400
You're going to be fine.

259
00:16:10,400 --> 00:16:11,500
Let's split when we get inside.

260
00:16:11,633 --> 00:16:13,500
So we can find
Mookie faster.

261
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:15,367
Let's go.

262
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:28,533
Wake up, baby girl.

263
00:16:31,900 --> 00:16:33,700
Mookie.

264
00:16:33,833 --> 00:16:35,533
Hi, Mookie.

265
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:39,200
Do you know who I am?

266
00:16:40,767 --> 00:16:43,867
Do you know
who I am in your life?

267
00:16:45,967 --> 00:16:47,767
You're Mommy Olive.

268
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:51,333
Yes. Yes!

269
00:16:51,467 --> 00:16:54,367
Yes, you're right, Mookie.

270
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:57,967
- It's me, my daughter!
- I'm not your daughter!

271
00:16:59,300 --> 00:17:01,833
I'm not your daughter!
Mommy Emma is my only mother!

272
00:17:01,967 --> 00:17:04,067
- I'm not your daughter!
- What?

273
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:06,467
I'm not your daughter!

274
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:10,267
I'm not your daughter!

275
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:13,433
Why do you still remember Emma?

276
00:17:13,567 --> 00:17:14,633
Why?

277
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:20,967
Astrid?

278
00:17:24,833 --> 00:17:27,833
Why does she still remember
Emma?

279
00:17:28,867 --> 00:17:30,300
I don't know.

280
00:17:32,833 --> 00:17:33,867
You don't know?

281
00:17:35,767 --> 00:17:40,800
Do you think I'm dumb?

282
00:17:40,933 --> 00:17:42,233
I don't know.

283
00:17:42,367 --> 00:17:44,333
What do you mean you don't know?

284
00:17:44,467 --> 00:17:47,167
Say something!

285
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:51,333
Do you think you can fool me?

286
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:52,933
Mommy, please.
Don't hurt Aunt Astrid.

287
00:17:53,067 --> 00:17:55,733
Did you really bring me
memaristol?

288
00:17:55,867 --> 00:17:58,000
The drug that erases memories?

289
00:17:58,133 --> 00:17:59,333
Answer me!

290
00:17:59,467 --> 00:18:00,633
You're hurting me.

291
00:18:00,767 --> 00:18:02,300
Answer me!

292
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:04,500
Don't dare lie to me!

293
00:18:04,633 --> 00:18:07,433
- You, traitor!
- Fine.

294
00:18:07,567 --> 00:18:08,933
Yes.

295
00:18:09,067 --> 00:18:11,633
I put in a different drug.

296
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:16,200
I brought a different drug.

297
00:18:16,333 --> 00:18:19,100
It's just a sedative.

298
00:18:20,133 --> 00:18:21,933
Mommy!

299
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:25,133
What right do you have
to interfere with my plans?

300
00:18:25,267 --> 00:18:27,000
You're just my assistant!

301
00:18:27,133 --> 00:18:29,633
- Please stop!
- Assistant!

302
00:18:29,767 --> 00:18:32,133
Yes!

303
00:18:32,267 --> 00:18:34,600
Assistant! Yes-man!

304
00:18:35,900 --> 00:18:37,033
I know!

305
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:41,500
Olive, enough. Let's stop this.

306
00:18:41,633 --> 00:18:45,000
I can no longer stomach
your wickedness.

307
00:18:45,133 --> 00:18:48,533
It's also a lie
that I'm happy you're alive.

308
00:18:50,633 --> 00:18:53,567
I thought I had gotten away
from you.

309
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:55,567
I've broken free
from the old Olive,

310
00:18:55,733 --> 00:18:58,233
the one I've long rejected!

311
00:18:58,367 --> 00:19:00,300
But I was wrong.

312
00:19:02,467 --> 00:19:03,733
Because...

313
00:19:04,433 --> 00:19:08,600
I tolerated your evilness.

314
00:19:08,733 --> 00:19:11,967
I was a fool to believe that you
would treat me as a friend.

315
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:14,633
I don't have a traitor friend!

316
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,933
Aunt Astrid!

317
00:19:22,067 --> 00:19:23,700
Auntie!

318
00:19:25,933 --> 00:19:27,467
Let go!

319
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:30,767
Olive, stop! Olive!

320
00:19:30,933 --> 00:19:34,767
Please stop! Please!

321
00:19:34,900 --> 00:19:37,000
Please stop!

322
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:41,300
Please, help!

323
00:19:41,433 --> 00:19:44,333
- Help!
- Stop it!

324
00:19:44,467 --> 00:19:47,400
- Let go!
- Stop it!

325
00:19:49,733 --> 00:19:51,167
Help.

326
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:00,100
Auntie!

327
00:20:03,167 --> 00:20:05,333
Aunt Astrid!

328
00:20:05,467 --> 00:20:06,767
Auntie!

329
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:11,633
Mommy! What did you do?

330
00:20:11,767 --> 00:20:14,733
- Astrid.
- Mommy!

331
00:20:14,867 --> 00:20:17,633
- Astrid!
- Aunt Astrid!

332
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:21,533
Emma?

333
00:20:27,733 --> 00:20:28,667
Emma?

334
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:30,733
Mookie?

335
00:20:33,600 --> 00:20:34,867
Emma!

336
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:35,933
Mookie!

337
00:20:37,467 --> 00:20:38,533
Emma!

338
00:20:42,033 --> 00:20:42,867
Emma?

339
00:20:43,933 --> 00:20:45,100
Mookie?

340
00:20:47,333 --> 00:20:48,433
Emma!

341
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:52,400
What's your business here, Boss?

342
00:20:52,533 --> 00:20:53,500
Wait.

343
00:20:53,633 --> 00:20:55,367
You seem lost.

344
00:20:58,200 --> 00:20:59,933
You're probably Olive's men.

345
00:21:00,067 --> 00:21:01,433
Hey!

346
00:21:02,633 --> 00:21:04,267
And so what?

347
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,833
You really are stubborn.

348
00:21:07,233 --> 00:21:08,300
Take care of him.

349
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:12,033
Boss...

350
00:21:12,167 --> 00:21:14,233
my daughter is in danger
in Olive's hands.

351
00:21:14,367 --> 00:21:16,300
If you still have
a little conscience left,

352
00:21:16,433 --> 00:21:18,233
you'll let me go.

353
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:40,800
- Astrid.
- Mommy!

354
00:21:40,933 --> 00:21:43,000
Mommy, what did you do?

355
00:21:43,167 --> 00:21:45,400
Mommy!

356
00:21:45,533 --> 00:21:49,667
Look what you're doing to us!

357
00:21:50,367 --> 00:21:52,967
You killed Aunt Astrid!

358
00:21:53,100 --> 00:21:55,933
You're so evil!

359
00:21:56,067 --> 00:21:58,700
Aunt Astrid!

360
00:21:58,833 --> 00:22:00,933
You're so evil!

361
00:22:01,067 --> 00:22:03,300
Evil!

362
00:22:03,433 --> 00:22:06,000
Astrid.

363
00:22:06,133 --> 00:22:09,233
Everything I said was true,
Astrid.

364
00:22:14,067 --> 00:22:16,800
I treated you like family.

365
00:22:21,233 --> 00:22:24,700
I hope you did what you said.

366
00:22:24,833 --> 00:22:28,400
That you chose me.

367
00:22:28,533 --> 00:22:32,033
And I wish you hadn't left me.

368
00:22:45,533 --> 00:22:49,433
But you kept betraying me.

369
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:56,300
So you should really die.

370
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:00,733
Just like any traitor.

371
00:23:02,033 --> 00:23:03,633
You deserve to die...

372
00:23:04,900 --> 00:23:07,433
and rot in hell!

373
00:23:15,333 --> 00:23:17,867
Farewell, my traitor friend!

374
00:23:20,333 --> 00:23:23,400
You're so evil!

375
00:23:28,733 --> 00:23:30,500
- You're so evil!
- Mookie!

376
00:23:30,633 --> 00:23:32,433
- Mom!
- Mookie!

377
00:23:32,567 --> 00:23:34,633
Mom, please help me.

378
00:23:37,433 --> 00:23:39,133
Congratulations!

379
00:23:41,033 --> 00:23:42,467
You've made it.

380
00:23:44,833 --> 00:23:46,800
You've made it to hell.

381
00:24:00,433 --> 00:24:02,867
I want to see Emma and Mookie.

382
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:06,600
Zayn and Flor
are with the rescue team.

383
00:24:06,733 --> 00:24:08,467
They're on their way
to Mookie and Emma.

384
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:12,033
I tried to be a loving mother,
a loving partner,

385
00:24:12,167 --> 00:24:13,300
and I failed.

386
00:24:13,433 --> 00:24:16,033
So this is the only way I know.

387
00:24:16,800 --> 00:24:18,933
Stop it, Mommy!

388
00:24:20,367 --> 00:24:22,333
Let go of me!

389
00:24:22,467 --> 00:24:23,333
Mommy!

390
00:24:23,467 --> 00:24:24,200
Emma!

391
00:24:25,167 --> 00:24:25,667
Emma!

392
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:38,400
Mom!
